"index_reference": "5226: basin",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A receptacle for liquids, often used for washing or purification rites.</p>\n<h2>Basins used as receptacles</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:22\">EXO 12:22</a></strong> <em>A basin is used to collect the blood of sacrifices.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod24:6\">EXO 24:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:5\">LEV 14:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:50\">LEV 14:50</a></p>\n<h2>Basins used for ritual washing</h2>\n<h3>Between the altar and the Tent of Meeting</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod30:18\">EXO 30:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod40:11\">EXO 40:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod40:30\">EXO 40:30</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev8:11\">LEV 8:11</a></p>\n<h3>In Solomon's temple</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr4:6\">2CH 4:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:30\">1KI 7:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:38\">1KI 7:38</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr4:14\">2CH 4:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs16:171\">2KI 16:171</a>KI <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs7:40\">7:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer52:17-Jer52:18\">JER 52:17–52:18</a></p>\n<h2>A basin used for ritual washing</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:5\">JHN 13:5</a></strong></p>",
